SMK Negeri 1 Mandiraja is a vocational high school In Mandiraja district, Banjarnegara Regency, Central Java province of Indonesia.
History.
SMK Negeri 1 Mandiraja School is a new school. It was established in 2010 at the request of the people in Mandiraja Sub-district. They wanted the construction of a vocational school in Mandiraja, School of State Vocational High School 1 Mandiraja.
Achievements.
State Vocational High school 1 Mandiraja has a variety of achievements at the district and provincial levels
